abstract: >
  A parallel Persian-language corpus of 4,000 records for benchmarking AI-generated
  text detection. Contains 1,000 human-written excerpts from pre-2020 Persian
  Wikipedia revisions, each paired with three AI-generated counterparts from
  DeepSeek v3.1, GPT-4o-mini, and Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite. The matched design — every
  topic generated by every model — enables fair cross-generator comparison and
  supports research on detection, generalization, and robustness in Persian NLP.
